Package: gnu-smalltalk
Architecture: any
Depends: libgst7 (= ${binary:Version}),
 gnu-smalltalk-common (= ${source:Version}),
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends}
Description: GNU Smalltalk interpreter
 GNU Smalltalk is an implementation of the Smalltalk-80 language. It uses a
 bytecode interpreter with a generational garbage collector and an optional
 JIT compiler via GNU Lightning.
 .
 This package contains the main interpreter binary (gst) and command-line
 tools for loading, packaging, testing, and profiling Smalltalk code.

Package: libgst7
Architecture: any
Section: libs
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends}
Description: GNU Smalltalk VM shared library
 GNU Smalltalk is an implementation of the Smalltalk-80 language.
 .
 This package contains the shared library for the GNU Smalltalk virtual
 machine (libgst), including the bytecode interpreter, garbage collector,
 and JIT compiler.

Package: libgst-dev
Architecture: any
Section: libdevel
Depends: libgst7 (= ${binary:Version}),
 ${misc:Depends}
Description: GNU Smalltalk development files
 GNU Smalltalk is an implementation of the Smalltalk-80 language.
 .
 This package contains header files, static libraries, pkg-config files,
 and autoconf macros needed for developing C extensions for GNU Smalltalk.

Package: gnu-smalltalk-common
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: GNU Smalltalk shared class library
 GNU Smalltalk is an implementation of the Smalltalk-80 language.
 .
 This package contains the architecture-independent Smalltalk class library,
 including .star package archives, kernel classes, and support scripts shared
 by all GNU Smalltalk binary packages.

Package: gnu-smalltalk-doc
Architecture: all
Section: doc
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: GNU Smalltalk documentation
 GNU Smalltalk is an implementation of the Smalltalk-80 language.
 .
 This package contains the GNU Smalltalk documentation in GNU Info format.

Package: gnu-smalltalk-browser
Architecture: all
Depends: gnu-smalltalk (>= ${source:Version}),
 libgtk4-gst (>= ${source:Version}),
 ${misc:Depends}
Suggests: libwebkitgtk-6.0-4
Description: VisualGST IDE for GNU Smalltalk (GTK4)
 GNU Smalltalk is an implementation of the Smalltalk-80 language.
 .
 This package contains VisualGST, a GTK4-based integrated development
 environment for GNU Smalltalk. It provides a class browser, workspace,
 inspector, debugger, and other Smalltalk development tools.
 .
 Optional: Install libwebkitgtk-6.0-4 to enable the built-in web browser
 (Smallzilla) and GTK documentation assistant.

Package: libgtk4-gst
Architecture: any
Section: libs
Depends: libgst7 (= ${binary:Version}),
 gnu-smalltalk-common (= ${source:Version}),
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends}
Description: GNU Smalltalk GTK4/GLib/Cairo bindings
 GNU Smalltalk is an implementation of the Smalltalk-80 language.
 .
 This package contains Smalltalk bindings for GTK4, GLib, GObject, Cairo,
 and the BLOX widget toolkit. It provides full access to GTK4 widgets and
 the GObject type system from Smalltalk code.

