Description: GNU Smalltalk GDBM database binding
 GNU Smalltalk is an implementation of the Smalltalk-80 language.
 .
 This package contains Smalltalk bindings for GDBM (GNU Database Manager),
 providing persistent key-value storage from Smalltalk.

